+## Voyage: next low tide
+
+Intent: Harbouemasters using the tide tool can ask for the next LOW tide after a given time,
+getting the time and height back, and a clear error when no upcoming low tide exists in the data.
+
+The existing high-tide path (`nextHighTide` in `src/tide.js`) serves as the pattern.
+The new function will be `nextLowTide`. The error message is "no upcoming low tide in data".
+
+Project has no `RIGGING.md` yet. Route to Shipwright for fitting out after specs are authored.
